14898 
14899 protected:
14921  template <class TElemType>
14922  void MetaDataChunkOfElem(const TElemType *elem,
14923  const unsigned long l,
14924  const unsigned long elemEnd,
14925  const unsigned short nElemSimul,
14926  const unsigned short nPadMin,
14927  unsigned long &lEnd,
14928  unsigned short &ind,
14929  unsigned short &llEnd,
14930  unsigned short &NPad) {
14931 
14932  /* Determine the end index for this chunk of elements that must be
14933  treated simulaneously. The elements of this chunk must have the
14934  same standard element in order to make this work. */
14935  const unsigned long lEndMax = min(l+nElemSimul, elemEnd);
14936 
14937  ind = elem[l].indStandardElement;
14938  for(lEnd=l+1; lEnd<lEndMax; ++lEnd) {
14939  if(elem[lEnd].indStandardElement != ind) break;
14940  }
14941 
14942  /* Store the number of elements that are treated simultaneously in this chunk
14943  in llEnd and determine the padded N value in the gemm computations. */
14944  llEnd = lEnd - l;
14945  NPad = llEnd*nVar;
14946  if( NPad%nPadMin ) NPad += nPadMin - (NPad%nPadMin);
14947  }
14948 };
